 行完就走, 唔走都唔好去村<br />\n有時唔做咁多嘢o架各位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"仲要齊上齊落 行完一定要走 唔好賴死唔走"},{"pid":"ebf2f491cb4eaaa4090a87efcb78d6d58fa4c8c3","tid":1360533,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:30:24.000Z","msg":"下面呢個post對727真係好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n727 非常關鍵。唯一一次不能各自爬山<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357976\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357976</a>"},{"pid":"e1edf2a8b9b14311455fb025dde2c1a6dbf34273","tid":1360533,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:34:56.000Z","msg":"今次元朗白衫恐襲呢單野，令到多左人有反黑警心態<br />\n加上搞到正常民生，更加多人忍唔住要出聲<br />\n連我自己D飲飲食食港女friend都日日睇元朗的新聞同記招<br />\n亦都因為咁呢兩日遍地開花嘅公務員支持post一浪接一浪<br />\n如果727呢次遊行做得好，一定可以幫我地集到唔少民氣！<br />\n再用更強大嘅民意去推5大訴求！！！"},{"pid":"d57de1978e6ca0582e94b739bdeb45826b241882","tid":1360533,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:39:06.000Z","msg":"上環都要睇！<br />\n<br />\n義士被爆頭 黑警開槍重創示威者<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355761</a>"},{"pid":"7e06faaf3e52dde3f53ecccfbfe0e258255e874f","tid":1360533,"uid":41364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"由得啲圍村佬自己嚇自己，我哋繼續保持和平高貴優雅"},{"pid":"107a55ddcae8705fc96d71aa850ba3781f99b841","tid":1360533,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44f2680ea7f2ce02fe4c68dfeb69e9864d62abc0","tid":1360533,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:18:56.000Z","msg":"係咪應該整返個whatsapp文宣反攻D廢老"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:43:02.000Z","msg":"推"}]}